25
00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:38.180
That's news to me!

26
00:02:38.180 --> 00:02:39.600
As it should be!

27
00:02:39.600 --> 00:02:41.560
Obviously I'm not the stella!

28
00:02:42.060 --> 00:02:43.310
The stella?

29
00:02:44.440 --> 00:02:46.480
I'm Punk-02,

30
00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:49.020
Vegapunk Lilith!

31
00:02:49.270 --> 00:02:53.490
Lilith the Evil

32
00:02:53.490 --> 00:02:55.570
Lilith? Punk-02?

33
00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:59.280
Our research budget is always tight!

34
00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:00.910
So, cough up your treasure!

35
00:03:00.910 --> 00:03:03.370
After that, I'll be on my way!

36
00:03:03.370 --> 00:03:04.370
What?!

37
00:03:04.370 --> 00:03:07.130
What are you talking about?!
This sea is freezing!

38
00:03:07.130 --> 00:03:10.460
If you're gonna save us,
you should follow through!

39
00:03:10.460 --> 00:03:11.920
I didn't mean to save you!

40
00:03:13.050 --> 00:03:17.050
It's supposed to be impossible
for any ship to enter these waters!

41
00:03:17.050 --> 00:03:21.890
We've got security in place
to sink anyone who tries!

42
00:03:38.030 --> 00:03:38.990
These here...

43
00:03:39.990 --> 00:03:42.870
sea beast weapons!

44
00:03:42.870 --> 00:03:44.950
Sea beast weapons?!

45
00:03:44.950 --> 00:03:46.080
Awesome!

46
00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:47.580
Never mind, I'm over this!

47
00:03:47.580 --> 00:03:48.790
Oh no!

48
00:03:49.380 --> 00:03:50.790
Robin!

49
00:03:54.010 --> 00:03:56.670
