132
00:08:05.010 --> 00:08:05.760
Listen!

133
00:08:05.760 --> 00:08:07.760
Rocket!

134
00:08:16.890 --> 00:08:18.560
That thing ate Luffy!

135
00:08:28.450 --> 00:08:31.030
Are you okay?! Luffy!

136
00:08:31.910 --> 00:08:33.990
Huh? I thought I got eaten...

137
