560
00:16:45.820 --> 00:16:50.240
You really expect me to believe this nonsense?

561
00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:53.780
Geniuses sure are a hassle.

562
00:16:54.830 --> 00:17:02.250
So our mission is to return this brat
to Egghead and eliminate all the Vegapunks.

563
00:16:56.950 --> 00:16:56.990
Kaku, Lucci, and Stussy
Cipher Pol Aigis 0
(Masked Assassins)

564
00:16:56.990 --> 00:16:57.030
Kaku, Lucci, and Stussy
Cipher Pol Aigis 0
(Masked Assassins)

565
00:16:57.030 --> 00:16:57.070
Kaku, Lucci, and Stussy
Cipher Pol Aigis 0
(Masked Assassins)

566
00:16:57.070 --> 00:16:57.120
Kaku, Lucci, and Stussy
Cipher Pol Aigis 0
(Masked Assassins)

567
00:16:57.120 --> 00:17:02.880
Kaku, Lucci, and Stussy
Cipher Pol Aigis 0
(Masked Assassins)

568
00:17:02.250 --> 00:17:04.710
The lab is full of valuable assets.

569
00:17:04.710 --> 00:17:07.010
Try not to damage them in the process.

570
00:17:07.010 --> 00:17:10.550
We're tasked with eliminating
the most useful man in the world.

571
00:17:10.550 --> 00:17:15.390
Does this have something to do with
what happened to Lulusia the other day?

572
00:17:15.390 --> 00:17:18.270
Don't be nosy.

573
00:17:18.270 --> 00:17:21.100
You're too sharp for your own good.

574
00:17:21.100 --> 00:17:22.650
I second that!

575
00:17:22.650 --> 00:17:26.150
Don't drag us into anything, Lucci!

576
00:17:27.900 --> 00:17:30.450
Oh man, that hit the spot!

577
00:17:30.450 --> 00:17:34.320
Everyone will be surprised
when they see the food machine.

578
00:17:34.320 --> 00:17:38.700
It's too bad they're not here yet. 
This thing is the best!

579
00:17:38.700 --> 00:17:41.460
Hey, do you think Sanji will get mad?

580
00:17:41.460 --> 00:17:43.210
You guys really pigged out!

581
00:17:43.210 --> 00:17:46.210
Your stomachs are all full to bursting!

582
00:17:46.210 --> 00:17:47.840
No, I always look like this.

583
00:17:47.840 --> 00:17:51.090
Recycollie

584
00:17:54.930 --> 00:17:56.720
Welp, gotta fly!

585
00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:58.560
Wait, you're leaving already?

586
00:17:58.560 --> 00:18:00.680
My job is to be violent!

587
00:18:00.680 --> 00:18:02.060
What kind of job is that?

588
00:18:18.740 --> 00:18:20.410
Who are they?

589
00:18:20.910 --> 00:18:22.790
Well, this is a lab...

590
00:18:22.790 --> 00:18:24.790
They must be researchers.

591
00:18:24.790 --> 00:18:28.250
The town was empty before,
but now they're coming out...

592
00:18:28.250 --> 00:18:32.470
Perhaps they were taking
precautions against us.

593
00:18:32.470 --> 00:18:36.050
Aren't those outfits kinda
heavy for a tropical island?

594
00:18:36.800 --> 00:18:37.600
Oh?

595
00:18:38.310 --> 00:18:39.100
Where's Luffy?

596
00:18:42.390 --> 00:18:43.850
There's your answer.

597
00:18:43.850 --> 00:18:44.980
What?!

598
00:18:44.980 --> 00:18:46.480
What are you doing?!

599
00:18:46.480 --> 00:18:48.570
Watch the hat!

600
00:18:49.190 --> 00:18:50.570
Luffy!

601
00:18:50.570 --> 00:18:51.900
Is he in there?

602
00:18:54.570 --> 00:18:56.700
Hey, guys!

603
00:18:56.700 --> 00:18:58.910
What do you think? How do I look?

604
00:19:03.210 --> 00:19:05.420
It's so weird!

605
00:19:05.830 --> 00:19:07.420
Isn't it heavy?

606
00:19:07.420 --> 00:19:09.290
It's really light, actually!

607
00:19:09.290 --> 00:19:11.760
And it keeps you cool!

608
00:19:12.130 --> 00:19:13.880
How fashionable.

609
00:19:13.880 --> 00:19:15.260
I want one, too!

610
00:19:15.260 --> 00:19:16.720
Where did you get it?

611
00:19:17.220 --> 00:19:18.220
This thing!

612
00:19:18.220 --> 00:19:20.510
They're giving us food and clothes?!

613
00:19:20.510 --> 00:19:22.470
This island is the best!

614
00:19:22.470 --> 00:19:25.440
To be honest, I've been feeling
sticky from that seawater!

615
00:19:25.440 --> 00:19:28.690
Please select your preferred attire.

616
00:19:28.690 --> 00:19:29.860
Preferred?

617
00:19:30.820 --> 00:19:32.360
Combat gear!

618
00:19:36.740 --> 00:19:38.990
I can take them off myself!

619
00:19:45.540 --> 00:19:47.250
You're right!

620
00:19:47.250 --> 00:19:48.540
They're super light!

621
00:19:48.540 --> 00:19:51.000
These shoes make me feel like I'm floating!

622
00:19:51.000 --> 00:19:52.460
This is awesome!

623
00:19:53.710 --> 00:19:54.800
The future!

624
00:19:54.800 --> 00:19:57.380
They even had a tropical style.

625
00:19:57.380 --> 00:19:59.760
You look great, Jinbe!

626
00:19:59.760 --> 00:20:03.100
Yeah? It's just right for a disguise.

627
00:20:03.100 --> 00:20:05.520
Although maybe we're past that point...

628
00:20:06.770 --> 00:20:11.150
Well, I'm gonna go find a weapon
and teach Vegapunk a lesson.

629
00:20:11.770 --> 00:20:12.770
See you.

630
00:20:12.770 --> 00:20:14.860
Take care of yourself, Bonney!

631
00:20:14.860 --> 00:20:16.530
Thanks a bunch!

632
00:20:24.910 --> 00:20:25.910
Hey!

633
00:20:30.500 --> 00:20:31.210
It's Kuma.

634
00:20:31.210 --> 00:20:32.540
Kuma?!

635
00:20:33.380 --> 00:20:37.380
Is it just me, or is he looking for us?

636
00:20:39.840 --> 00:20:40.640
Guys, move!

637
00:20:41.550 --> 00:20:42.680
What?!

638
00:20:43.100 --> 00:20:44.640
He's gonna charge!

639
00:20:45.600 --> 00:20:47.140
He's after us!

640
00:20:47.140 --> 00:20:47.850
Hey!

641
00:20:51.940 --> 00:20:54.270
What's going on? Fill me in!

642
00:20:54.270 --> 00:20:55.900
Just keep running!

643
00:20:57.070 --> 00:20:58.150
Oh, crap!

644
00:21:07.410 --> 00:21:10.670
Dine and dash. Shoplifting.

645
00:21:14.340 --> 00:21:16.300
Here comes the laser!

646
00:21:23.930 --> 00:21:26.810
I didn't know I needed to pay!
It came out when I kicked it!

647
00:21:26.810 --> 00:21:28.680
That's vandalism, Luffy.

648
00:21:34.860 --> 00:21:37.480
They're gonna kill us over a dine and dash?!

649
00:21:37.480 --> 00:21:39.190
It is a bit excessive.

650
00:21:43.620 --> 00:21:46.280
We gotta fight back or we're in trouble!

651
00:21:46.280 --> 00:21:50.040
We may be pirates, but this is self-defense.

652
00:21:50.040 --> 00:21:52.960
Alright! I didn't want to do this, but...

653
00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:15.440
Gum-Gum...

654
00:22:22.490 --> 00:22:23.860
Wait!

655
00:22:34.170 --> 00:22:36.210
Hey! What's your problem, Bonney?!

656
00:22:36.210 --> 00:22:39.800
If he's gonna shoot lasers,
at least let me punch–

657
00:22:49.930 --> 00:22:51.600
That's my dad...

658
00:22:54.980 --> 00:22:56.690
The only...

659
00:23:00.030 --> 00:23:01.990
family I have left!

660
00:23:01.990 --> 00:23:03.700
What?!

661
00:23:08.620 --> 00:23:11.370
Your dad who was turned into a cyborg...

662
00:23:11.370 --> 00:23:13.540
...is Kuma?!

663
00:23:32.310 --> 00:23:34.310
So please!

664
00:23:34.310 --> 00:23:37.190
Don't hurt my daddy!

665
00:23:37.190 --> 00:23:38.810
Run, you dummy!

666
00:23:38.810 --> 00:23:40.520
It's a pacifista!

667
00:23:43.740 --> 00:23:44.950
Bonney!

668
00:23:44.950 --> 00:23:46.400
Bonney!

669
00:23:52.290 --> 00:23:56.250
A Stretch of Sea
New World

670
00:24:03.710 --> 00:24:05.720
Close valve two!

671
00:24:05.720 --> 00:24:07.840
Seal it, quickly!

672
00:24:08.510 --> 00:24:10.100
Here, too!

673
00:24:12.310 --> 00:24:13.770
Something dead ahead!

674
00:24:14.140 --> 00:24:15.520
Dodge it!

675
00:24:21.060 --> 00:24:23.820
It's no good, Captain!
We can't give them the slip!

676
00:24:36.620 --> 00:24:39.170
As if I'd let you escape!

677
00:24:48.550 --> 00:24:51.890
One more hit like that,
and the water pressure will crush the ship!

678
00:24:52.260 --> 00:24:53.720
No getting away now!

679
00:24:59.560 --> 00:25:00.600
Let's surface.

680
00:25:01.230 --> 00:25:03.730
To the nearby shore! Head northeast!

681
00:25:03.730 --> 00:25:05.070
– Aye aye, Captain!
– Aye aye, Captain!

682
00:25:05.070 --> 00:25:06.990
Head for land!

683
00:25:06.990 --> 00:25:09.450
Hard to starboard!

684
00:25:15.450 --> 00:25:17.830
Prepare for battle! Hurry!

685
00:25:22.080 --> 00:25:24.290
What happened to me?

686
00:25:24.790 --> 00:25:27.050
Anyway, we're in trouble!

687
00:25:27.050 --> 00:25:29.760
– You're so cute, Captain!
– You're so cute, Captain!

688
00:25:29.760 --> 00:25:31.970
Say that again and I'll end you!

689
00:25:32.760 --> 00:25:34.550
– But you are!
– But you are!

690
00:25:36.060 --> 00:25:37.560
Oh, crap!

691
00:25:37.560 --> 00:25:38.810
Even I...

692
00:25:41.020 --> 00:25:43.020
My sex has been changed!

693
00:25:43.400 --> 00:25:45.360
Don't touch the infected!

694
00:25:45.360 --> 00:25:47.190
S-Sorry...

695
00:25:47.190 --> 00:25:50.110
It's an ability that spreads infections!

696
00:25:50.110 --> 00:25:52.280
It changes your sex!

697
00:25:54.030 --> 00:25:57.950
I learned something in my battles
against the Emperors, though.

698
00:25:57.950 --> 00:25:59.950
It's possible to break through it!

699
00:26:00.540 --> 00:26:02.500
If you use enough haki...

700
00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:05.210
you can nullify devil fruit powers!

701
00:26:20.600 --> 00:26:22.350
We surfaced, Captain!

702
00:26:23.560 --> 00:26:25.440
I'm cured!

703
00:26:27.150 --> 00:26:28.230
Good.

704
00:26:28.230 --> 00:26:30.490
That's our captain!

705
00:26:30.490 --> 00:26:32.650
There's no time to relax.

706
00:26:33.030 --> 00:26:35.160
Dock the ship! We're going ashore!

707
00:26:35.160 --> 00:26:36.620
– Aye aye, sir!
– Aye aye, sir!

708
00:26:42.910 --> 00:26:45.170
He managed to cure the disease, huh?

709
00:26:45.540 --> 00:26:48.290
Guess he lives up to that
three-billion-berry bounty.

710
00:26:48.290 --> 00:26:49.420
That's right.

711
00:26:49.420 --> 00:26:54.630
The antibodies of the cured spread
just like the disease itself.

712
00:26:56.140 --> 00:26:59.890
I trust you enjoyed my feminization disease.

713
00:26:59.890 --> 00:27:02.350
Doc Q
(Sick-Sick Fruit)

714
00:27:04.190 --> 00:27:07.060
Burgess! Let's move to the island.

715
00:27:07.060 --> 00:27:09.570
Van Augur
(Warp-Warp Fruit)

716
00:27:09.570 --> 00:27:11.030
Right on!

717
00:27:20.620 --> 00:27:23.250
What?! The mountain is moving!

718
00:27:23.250 --> 00:27:26.210
Hey! There's someone deep in the island!

719
00:27:39.350 --> 00:27:43.100
These Strong-Strong Fruit powers are the best!

720
00:27:43.100 --> 00:27:45.560
Jesus Burgess
(Strong-Strong Fruit)

721
00:27:45.560 --> 00:27:47.190
Burgess?!

722
00:27:47.190 --> 00:27:50.480
How is he picking up an entire mountain?!

723
00:27:50.480 --> 00:27:52.940
When did they even get here?!

724
00:27:53.570 --> 00:27:55.320
It must be another devil fruit.

725
00:27:55.700 --> 00:27:58.780
Superhuman strength,
contagion, teleportation:

726
00:27:58.780 --> 00:28:02.700
Devil-fruit hunting has landed
them some ridiculous powers!

727
00:28:02.700 --> 00:28:05.210
No wonder their bounties keep going up!

728
00:28:16.340 --> 00:28:17.680
Room!

729
00:28:23.810 --> 00:28:25.350
Amputate!

730
00:28:57.010 --> 00:29:00.720
Long time no see, Trafalgar Law!

731
00:29:00.720 --> 00:29:02.680
Blackbeard!

732
00:29:02.680 --> 00:29:03.930
Why are you here?!

733
00:29:03.930 --> 00:29:05.560
Don't be like that!

734
00:29:05.560 --> 00:29:08.140
We're both members of the Worst Generation!

735
00:29:12.900 --> 00:29:13.900
Commodore!

736
00:29:15.020 --> 00:29:18.030
Stronger says you're too heavy...

737
00:29:18.030 --> 00:29:19.240
and I agree...

738
00:29:22.320 --> 00:29:24.700
Stronger
(Horse-Horse Fruit: Pegasus
Mythical Type)

739
00:29:24.700 --> 00:29:27.450
Between you, Straw Hat, and Kid...

740
00:29:27.450 --> 00:29:32.170
I knew one of you would be
coming here from Wano!

741
00:29:32.630 --> 00:29:35.340
I can't believe Kaido and Big Mom went down!

742
00:29:35.340 --> 00:29:37.960
The world has been turned upside down!

743
00:29:37.960 --> 00:29:40.130
And I'm loving it!

744
00:29:43.720 --> 00:29:47.430
Of course, Kaido had one, didn't he?

745
00:29:49.390 --> 00:29:52.150
How many have you guys found?

746
00:29:52.150 --> 00:29:56.610
I'll be helping myself
to all of your lode poneglyphs!

747
00:29:59.820 --> 00:30:02.030
Right back at you!

748
00:30:08.040 --> 00:30:09.620
The winner...

749
00:30:10.040 --> 00:30:11.830
takes all!
